0.003002	2026-01-20

 [ Bug Fixes ]
 - Bump Class::XSConstructor dependency for FOREIGNBUILDARGS fix.

 [ Other ]
 - Better detection of what should be considered a foreign class than
   Class::XSConstructor has built in.

0.003001	2026-01-17

 [ Documentation ]
 - Include more SEE ALSO links.

 [ Packaging ]
 - Bump Class::XSConstructor dependency.

0.003000	2026-01-13

 - Updated: Also create an XS DESTROY method.
 - Updated: Use more recent version of Class::XSConstructor which supports
   more features of Moo, so should be able to provide XS constructors
   almost always.

0.002	2020-02-19

 [ Bug Fixes ]
 - Fix warning when inheriting from a non-Moo base class.

